{"tid":1455841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，佢清場，我地就去反包圍！","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:38:52.000Z","uid":78184,"like":14,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"26dbf4ea12fcfb0c1e80b6eced64140ea528108d","tid":1455841,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:26:15.000Z","msg":"仲未收工、在路上的香港人，機場明顯準備一陣會開大波，可能會係入面大拘捕。斷哂網絡同埋直播，做乜都無人知。<br />\n<br />\n我地係出面的香港人，唔會乜都做唔到，因為我地仲有幾十萬人可以入機場反包圍，同班仆街來一場真戰鬥，人多終勝！<br />\n<br />\n幫手推上熱門，為721 811的受害者討回公義！"},{"pid":"d7a20741c6c3d2540ba86ea5abe1014d437afac8","tid":1455841,"uid":113784,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:26:53.000Z","msg":"1. 我哋目的係向外宣傳，冇機冇旅客，等於冇宣傳<br />\n<br />\n2. 我哋目的可能係癱瘓機場，依家所有班機都取消，已經癱瘓咗機場<br />\n<br />\n留低有咩做？？自己問下自己。<br />\n<br />\n到時機場回復運作咪再入過囉，更加唔好講夜晚收工接力的手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5efbfb6d7b8bf6b2393b3a1b38e65ce750fea92","tid":1455841,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:27:12.000Z","msg":"無旅客即係無得宣傳啦<br />\n無得宣傳咪走囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0acea4e74315b2747a4edbadbf84be4f09a4ec61","tid":1455841,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:27:33.000Z","msg":"入去救人呀"},{"pid":"5c53fc15c4780e45618ba4dc651d2f4fb894edde","tid":1455841,"uid":178042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:27:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0b6e085e253298d46adf5784b1515443a387e1b9","tid":1455841,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:28:08.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"2bb364d0d1f6cf60475d7178804b5e34fc979423","tid":1455841,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0acea4e74315b2747a4edbadbf84be4f09a4ec61","tid":1455841,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"